OL,3,CDoctors and dentists in Wales given 4%
OL,4,Cpay rise as NHS pay awards announced
OL,6,FThe independent review by the NHS Pay
OL,7,FReview Body also made additional
OL,8,Frecommendations outside of pay, which
OL,9,Fwill be considered separately.
OL,11,FIt was also announced that while pay
OL,12,Frises for primary care workers
OL,13,Fincluding community pharmacies, NHS
OL,14,Foptometry and all staff working in
OL,15,Fgeneral practice and dental teams was
OL,16,Foutside the scope of the
OL,17,Frecommendations, the Welsh Government
OL,18,Fsaid it wants to see a "fair and
OL,19,Fproportionate" rise across this sector.
