OL,3,CDoctors and dentists in Wales given 4%
OL,4,Cpay rise as NHS pay awards announced
OL,6,FJeremy Miles added: "While falling
OL,7,Foutside the scope of the DDRB
OL,8,Frecommendations, we want to see a fair
OL,9,Fand proportionate pay uplift across
OL,10,Fprimary care, including community
OL,11,Fpharmacies, NHS optometry and all
OL,12,Fstaff working in general practice and
OL,13,Fdental teams.
OL,15,F"This is in recognition of the vital
OL,16,Frole primary care, and its staff,
OL,17,Fplays in delivering essential services
OL,18,Fto people throughout Wales.
