OL,3,CDoctors and dentists in Wales given 4%
OL,4,Cpay rise as NHS pay awards announced
OL,6,F"The DDRB and Welsh Government fail to
OL,7,Frecognise that doctors continue to
OL,8,Fexperience the worst pay erosion in
OL,9,Fthe public sector, which is not
OL,10,Facceptable. Similarly, the
OL,11,Funderfunding of the GMS contract
OL,12,Fleaves general practice in a
OL,13,Fprecarious position, with financial
OL,14,Fremedy required immediately.
