OL,3,CDoctors and dentists in Wales given 4%
OL,4,Cpay rise as NHS pay awards announced
OL,6,F"Doctors are trying to get through the
OL,7,Flongest waiting lists on record and
OL,8,Fsacrificing their own health to do so,
OL,9,Fwith high levels of exhaustion and
OL,10,Fburnout reported. Now more than ever,
OL,11,Fdoctors need pay restoration, which
OL,12,Fwill help the profession feel
OL,13,Fappreciated for routinely going above
OL,14,Fand beyond.
OL,16,F"We will now digest the DDRB report
OL,17,Fand further consult with our members
OL,18,Fto gauge their views and consider our
OL,19,Fnext steps. We have requested an
OL,20,Furgent meeting with the Cabinet
OL,21,FSecretary."
